{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775864540157,"sessionID":"ses_28639ccf8ffe7QosoZNnrspyzA","part":{"id":"prt_d79c66728001LY3fIT0SLvoSHU","messageID":"msg_d79c65f19001TeYWW4alpTAM34","sessionID":"ses_28639ccf8ffe7QosoZNnrspyzA","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-2f42b35f229541b996b41845b8a37ec9","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/CHANGE.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/CHANGE.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n2: \n3: ## Metadata\n4: - **AR**: AR-019\n5: - **Title**: CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n6: - **Module**: cmd\n7: - **Language**: Go\n8: - **Size**: M\n9: - **Status**: Completed\n10: \n11: ## Description\n12: \n13: Implemented 4 CLI binary entry points for managing AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter Kubernetes resources:\n14: \n15: 1. **agentcube** - Main unified CLI with subcommands for managing both resource types\n16: 2. **agent-runtime** - Dedicated CLI for AgentRuntime resource operations\n17: 3. **code-interpreter** - Dedicated CLI for CodeInterpreter resource operations\n18: 4. **agentcube-util** - Utility CLI for validation, diagnostics, and completion generation\n19: \n20: ## Dependencies\n21: \n22: - github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/cli\n23: - github.com/spf13/cobra\n24: - gopkg.in/yaml.v3\n25: - k8s.io/client-go\n26: - k8s.io/apimachinery\n27: \n28: ## Related Changes\n29: \n30: None\n31: \n32: ## Implementation Notes\n33: \n34: All binaries build successfully and support the following features:\n35: \n36: - Common flags: --kubeconfig, --namespace, --output\n37: - CRUD operations: list, get, create, update, delete, watch\n38: - Output formats: table, json, yaml\n39: - Shell completion: bash, zsh, fish, powershell\n40: - Error handling with user-friendly messages\n41: \n42: ## Deferred Items\n43: \n44: The following items were deferred for future implementation:\n45: \n46: - Unit tests for all binaries\n47: - Integration tests\n48: - Static analysis (go vet, gofmt)\n49: - Makefile build targets\n50: - README documentation for each binary\n51: - Environment variable support testing\n52: - Project documentation updates\n\n(End of file - total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n\n## Metadata\n- **AR**: AR-019\n- **Title**: CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n- **Module**: cmd\n- **Language**: Go\n- **Size**: M\n- **Status**: Completed\n\n## Description\n\nImplemented 4 CLI binary entry points for managing AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter Kubernetes resources:\n\n1. **agentcube** - Main unified CLI with subcommands for managing both resource types\n2. **agent-runtime** - Dedicated CLI for AgentRuntime resource operations\n3. **code-interpreter** - Dedicated CLI for CodeInterpreter resource operations\n4. **agentcube-util** - Utility CLI for validation, diagnostics, and completion generation\n\n## Dependencies","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/changes/AR-019/CHANGE.md","time":{"start":1775864540132,"end":1775864540155}}}}
